  Home -->|GET /api/cars| API_CARS
  Cars -->|GET /api/cars| API_CARS
  CarDetails -->|GET /api/car/:id| API_CAR_ID
  Bookings -->|GET /api/myBooking (auth)| API_MYBOOKING
  Bookings -->|POST /api/new/booking (auth)| API_NEWBOOKING
  Home -->|POST /new/visiter| API_VISITER

